urgent help w getting rid of fleas inside the house does any one know how to kill fleas inside a house without using bug bombs thanks a vetrinarian taught me a trick to at least cut down on flea infestation and reinfestation first make sure all pets have been treated next the vet recommended i set up a few bowls of water in key areas of carpeting in the house then shine a goose neck or other kind of desk lamp that can be aimed at the bowls of water fleas will be attracted to the heat of the lamps and jump up towards it they come down into the water and subsequently drown you might be surprised at just how many dead fleas you find each morning Aladdin (1992 film) Bedbug Dial M for Murder Flea Blood (computer game) Fluorescent lamp Cat Bubble Bobble Sonic the Hedgehog (16-bit) The Dalek Invasion of Earth RuneScape quests Suicide methods Mahou Sentai Magiranger Plagues of Egypt Pet skunk Domestic rabbit Drowning Lighting Fast bowling Bat Collar The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time places Worms weapons and tools Lava lamp Columbine High School massacre The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Tertiary to Quintessential Phases Bong Flea market Ranma __ characters Naruto jutsu The Amber Spyglass Swimming Linked list Chinchilla Myxomatosis Beetle Manila Heartworm The Shining (film) Bat Boy Mouse (computing) Mid-levels Bowls Baylisascaris Snowboarding Butters Stotch Dundas Square Halo: Combat Evolved The Subtle Knife Ultraviolet Scabies Diwali Japanese tea ceremony Conspiracy (TNG episode) Syphon Filter Diseases of the honeybee Schistosomiasis IBM PC compatible Vegeta Discovery Bay Super Bowl XVII Poker jargon P. G. Wodehouse Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Dog collar Glossary of American football Red Hot Chili Peppers (album) Sea-Monkey Kakapo Piccolo Junior Saga Bubonic plague Super Bowl III Basement Alabaster Super Bowl XXI Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Tiny Toon Adventures Carnivorous plant The SpongeBob SquarePants Movie 101 Dalmatians: The Series Coconut crab Slugg